}},{"text":"有富余时分享一些","scores":{"generosity":1}},{"text":"精打细算，优先自己需要","scores":{"generosity":0}},{"text":"不太愿意分享稀缺资源","scores":{"generosity":-1}}]},{"id":"q36","dimension":"creativity","subDimension":"originality","text":"看到别人有很酷的装扮搭配，你会？","options":[{"text":"受到启发，创造自己的风格","scores":{"originality":2}},{"text":"学习借鉴，搭配类似的","scores":{"originality":0}},{"text":"问问对方是怎么搭配的","scores":{"originality":1}},{"text":"欣赏但不模仿，坚持自己的风格","scores":{"originality":1}}]},{"id":"q37","dimension":"adventure","subDimension":"speed","text":"跑图时，你更注重？","options":[{"text":"速度效率，最短时间最多烛火","scores":{"speed":2}},{"text":"边跑边欣赏风景","scores":{"speed":-1}},{"text":"和朋友一起，效率其次","scores":{"speed":0}},{"text":"随性而行，没有固定路线","scores":{"speed":-2}}]},{"id":"q38","dimension":"spirit","subDimension":"presence","text":"你在游戏时通常的状态是？","options":[{"text":"全身心投入，享受当下","scores":{"presence":2}},{"text":"专注完成任务，其他不太在意","scores":{"presence":1}},{"text":"边玩游戏边做其他事","scores":{"presence":-1}},{"text":"有些心不在焉","scores":{"presence":-2}}]},{"id":"q39","dimension":"social","subDimension":"inclusion","text":"当有新玩家加入你们的小队时，你会？","options":[{"text":"热情欢迎，主动带他们融入","scores":{"inclusion":2}},{"text":"友好对待，等他们自己适应","scores":{"inclusion":1}},{"text":"继续和熟悉的朋友互动","scores":{"inclusion":0}},{"text":"比较被动，等待对方先示好","scores":{"inclusion":-1}}]},{"id":"q40","dimension":"creativity","subDimension":"imagination","text":"在光遇的世界里，你会？","options":[{"text":"经常脑补剧情，创造自己的故事","scores":{"imagination":2}},{"text":"偶尔想象一些有趣的场景","scores":{"imagination":1}},{"text":"专注于游戏本身的内容","scores":{"imagination":0}},{"text":"很少做这种想象","scores":{"imagination":-1}}]},{"id":"q41","dimension":"adventure","subDimension":"exploration","text":"对于游戏中的季节任务，你的完成方式是？","options":[{"text":"第一天就全部完成","scores":{"exploration":2}},{"text":"每天按时完成当天的任务","scores":{"exploration":1}},{"text":"累积几天再一起完成","scores":{"exploration":0}},{"text":"快结束前才匆忙完成","scores":{"exploration":-1}}]},{"id":"q42","dimension":"spirit","subDimension":"wisdom","text":"从光遇中学到的东西，你会？","options":[{"text":"应用到现实