es":{"goal":2}},{"text":"和朋友一起快乐游戏","scores":{"goal":1}},{"text":"体验游戏故事和世界","scores":{"goal":1}},{"text":"放松心情，没有具体目标","scores":{"goal":0}}]},{"id":"q50","dimension":"spirit","subDimension":"acceptance","text":"对于游戏中的失去（如好友退游、错过限定），你会？","options":[{"text":"坦然接受，珍惜当下拥有的","scores":{"acceptance":2}},{"text":"有些遗憾，但能调整心态","scores":{"acceptance":1}},{"text":"需要一段时间接受","scores":{"acceptance":0}},{"text":"会难过一段时间","scores":{"acceptance":-1}}]},{"id":"q51","dimension":"social","subDimension":"mentorship","text":"如果有机会带萌新，你会？","options":[{"text":"非常愿意，耐心教导","scores":{"mentorship":2}},{"text":"愿意，但可能不太有耐心","scores":{"mentorship":1}},{"text":"看情况，有时间就帮","scores":{"mentorship":0}},{"text":"更喜欢自己玩游戏","scores":{"mentorship":-1}}]},{"id":"q52","dimension":"creativity","subDimension":"documentation","text":"你会记录自己在光遇的经历吗？","options":[{"text":"会写日记或发动态记录","scores":{"documentation":2}},{"text":"拍照片视频保存回忆","scores":{"documentation":1}},{"text":"偶尔截图保存","scores":{"documentation":0}},{"text":"不太记录，活在当下","scores":{"documentation":-1}}]}]}